column5: Here are my latest videos I will be trying to get the rest done tomorrow
Damn !!!! What a way to start my day Great vids Mike!!!
Some fine fins and footage there Mike! Congrats to you and thanks for sharing those gems.
Great fishing there mike! Just one question, why can you musky fishermen never smile?
Cause the fish are so damn heavy...lol... Have to concentrate on balancing the floppy 30 pounds of muscle with razor blades for teeth...
Great videos Mike! I especially like the still shots with Jade hamming it up for the camera!!! LOL!!!
Awesome videos Mike. That is one hell of a day.  I think I am going to have to take a trip down there and try for some muskie.
Thanks all.  Chris that is my smile look at my eyes they are squinting so I must be smiling.  Brian jade sure is a nut.  I will have some more soon from the weekend
